**C1 (tray navigate)**: When tray navigates, `popToRoot()` + `push()` is called. Since RootSearchView only renders when `!currentNavData`, the push causes RootSearchView to unmount. When user later navigates back, it remounts with fresh `useState` defaults. **Not actually a bug** — unmount handles the reset.

